Amazing documentary. must see if you like fighting and have a brain

Ad torrent: Flawless video & audio

Ad movie: Interesting and amusing, but some of the conclusions that the "scientists" arrive to must be taken with reserve. After all, they test only one speciman from every sport. So claims such as "kung fu is the fastest" or "tae kwon do has best reaction times" are a little stretch, based on comparison between two people. However, the documentary is still fun to watch. I recommend to all martial arts fans.
